      "span_text": "A schematic view of the SOI MOS device structures used in the experiments is shown in Figure 1  ; the SOI layer (t S ) is 30 nm thick, the gate oxide layer (t OX ) is 7 nm thick, the buried-oxide (BOX) layer (t BOX ) is 80 nm thick, the body-doping concentration (N A ) is 5 × 10 17 cm −3 (n-ch MOSFET) or 4 × 10 17 cm −3 (p-ch MOSFET) of acceptor Boron atoms, and the gate length (L G ) is 0.1 m or 1.0 m.",
